                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>\n                                        <date>5<hi rend=\"sup\">th</hi> Feby. 54</date>.</p>\n                              <p>Dr. &amp; Rev. Sir!</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Our friend <persName>Dr. Illowy</persName> sent\n                                        me<lb/> the <sic>inclosed</sic> Hebrew paper. I\n                                                  began<add>?</add> to translate<lb/> but find that\n                                        it will take up <sic>mor</sic> time than<lb/> I have to\n                                        spare, and gives more laborer than<lb/> the subject is worth\n                                        especially as I do not think<lb/> it wise to raise any\n                                        quacking <add>?</add> to the<lb/> dignity of martyrdom. I\n                                        therefore send the papers<lb/> back: But as <persName>Dr.\n                                                  Illowy</persName> has not given me any<lb/>\n                                        address, I take the liberty of <sic>inclosing</sic> them\n                                        to<lb/> your care, with a request to have them to him<lb/>\n                                        at yr earliest convenience &amp; oblige</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">Dr &amp; Rev Sir</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(9)\">yours very Respfy</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">MJRaphall</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>\n                                        <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3bz61v2m/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
